01:05:52.756 --> 01:05:54.394
<font color="#00ffff">den Behörden</font>
<font color="#00ffff">das Gesicht zeigen muss,</font>

1121
01:05:55.036 --> 01:05:57.061
<font color="#00ffff">wenn das</font>
